HOWTO, create a new release directory
*************************************

- create the directory

- create a script sh create_XXX_release.sh (see LFMM/create_XXX_release.sh for example)

- create a meta directory, (see LFMM/meta for example).
This meta directory contains all the common structure of the release.
Usually, there are directories code, examples, documentation, bin 
and files for install and README.

Do not foget to update the READMEÂ and the makefile if necessary.
